ivardefs.name: actor
ivardefs.desc: A Person, Location/HealthcareService or Device that is participating in the appointment.

ivardefs.name: appointment
ivardefs.desc: Appointment that this response is replying to.

ivardefs.name: end
ivardefs.desc: This may be either the same as the appointment request to confirm the details of the appointment, or alternately a new time to request a re-negotiation of the end time.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: This records identifiers associated with this appointment response concern that are defined by business processes and/ or used to refer to it when a direct URL reference to the resource itself is not appropriate.

ivardefs.name: participantStatus
ivardefs.desc: Participation status of the participant. When the status is declined or tentative if the start/end times are different to the appointment, then these times should be interpreted as a requested time change. When the status is accepted, the times can either

ivardefs.name: participantType_
ivardefs.desc: Role of participant in the appointment.

ivardefs.name: start
ivardefs.desc: Date/Time that the appointment is to take place, or requested new start time.
